{"tid":2514862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真。國安非禮女護士","createTime":"2021-05-03T13:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T13:51:40.000Z","uid":101945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ff218d177c647a9667a1adb20ced2668c037abe","tid":2514862,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"五旬診所醫生被指在私家車上非禮一名年輕診所女護士，案件今(3日)在九龍城法院審理，女事主因應考文憑試，其母親出庭講述女兒提及事發經過，指被告當日疑為開解患有抑鬱症的女事主，特別駕車載女事主到尖沙咀午餐，期間被告曾牽女事主的手，又摸女事主的背部至臀部，並曾問女事主可否當其女友。至二人離開時，被告又趁幫女事主繫安全帶時摸其胸，維時約30秒。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">被告關國安</span></strong>，被控一項非禮罪，指他於2020年3月14日，在尖沙咀海運大廈停車場及其私家車內猥褻侵犯女子X。"},{"pid":"e5c9c9ef27896c2e816d6fc329acad9ef4860764","tid":2514862,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRZGTmhXvdyNnsvfu9vuo6ErfyR9AeV2aJ6iTR5fN9Dxw?filename=fWAS4cT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWAS4cT.gif&h=a38ae283&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a008c5991f606cfde14ed84ff843f214e8721b3","tid":2514862,"uid":250308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:50:15.000Z","msg":"全名叫關國安鬼事"},{"pid":"811c50b5d64f0f1ec19566fbc6aeda4d3a2c5e87","tid":2514862,"uid":134149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:51:40.000Z","msg":"關國安咩事"}]}